Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Modern office and warehouse complex that forms part of the well known Century Estate Development.

Located in the prominent industrial suburb of Welshpool some 10 kilometres south east of the Perth CBD and more specifically on the strategic corner of Kewdale Road and Dowd Street.

Office tenancies available:

Level 1, Unit 3A - 186.25sqm
Fully refurbished, open plan, self contained office tenancy.

Level 1, Unit 14A - 119.77sqm
Partly partitioned, self contained office tenancy.

Minimum 5 year lease term.
Ample open air parking available. Undercover carbays available at a rate of $50/bay pcm.

Fully self contained first floor office premises with new paint and floor coverings.

Superbly located within Kewdale, Perth's premier commercial and industrial precinct, within 12 kilometres and 20 minutes from the CBD.

Excellent exposure with in excess of 28,000 vehicles passing the property on an average week day, direct links to major arterial roads including Orrong, Abernethy and Welshpool Roads, Leach, Roe and Tonkin Highways and Graham Farmer Freeway. Strategic proximity to transport services, interstate rail freight terminal, domestic and international airports.

Area: 180 sqm
Rent: $315/sqm + GST
Outgoings: $31.24/sqm per annum + GST
Car Parking: Ample open air car bays available at no cost. Allocated undercover car bays available at a rate of $50/bay per calendar month

For further details please contact Kendall Forrest on 0439 700 717.

This high quality commercial and retail development is under construction and will be positioned in a a landscaped parkland environment off Horrie Miller Drive in Kewdale.

Stage 1 will comprise 1,300sqm of first floor office with ground floor retail operators to include an IGA Express, Subway, Dome Cafe, Newsagency, Liquor store and other retail/food outlets.

"Gate 1" will be situated on the key gateway site of Kewlink East on Horrie Miller Drive, the main access road to Perth's International Terminal. Situated 20 minutes east of Perth's CBD and near major arterial roads such as Tonkin and Roe Highway's.

Level 1 office space available;
Unit A16 - 308 sqm

Ground floor tenancies available of 100-700sqm.

Asking rent - $325/sqm net
Outgoings - Estimated at a rate of $75/sqm per annum
Availability - Immediate

Internal finishes include suspended ceiling tiles with lighting and air-conditioning, carpets and paint.

For further information please contact Kendall Forrest on 0439 700 717 or kendall.forrest@cbre.com.au
